IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User epandurski@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass gmail/mbsync"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPAccount swaptacular
Host mail.your-server.de
User epandurski@swaptacular.org
PassCmd "pass hetzner/mbsync"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

IMAPStore swaptacular-remote
Account swaptacular

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/Gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/Gmail/Inbox

MaildirStore swaptacular-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/Swaptacular/
Inbox ~/Mail/Swaptacular/Inbox

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]/Drafts
Create Both
SyncState *

Channel swaptacular
Far :swaptacular-remote:
Near :swaptacular-local:
Patterns * !Drafts
Create Both
SyncState *
